hi i am fariyaj shaikh i am learning git and i wirte the same comman git cammand or steps
1 - install gitbash from website
2 - crete github account 
3 - in linux use this cammand $ apt install git
4 - check version by using $ git --version
5 - frist $ git init --initilising git from local repositry
6 - git config --global user.email "____"
7 - git config --global user.name "____"
8 - git config --list ---showing the all file
9 - git clone <url> -- download code or file from website
10 - git add . -- add all or git add <name of file>
11 -git commit -m "write down reson  why do to update this code or file" <name of file> ---save the file in local repo.
12 - git log ---check for commit
13 - git log --online
14 - git push <name of file> -- send the file from local repo. to the github account
15 - git branch --check yhe current barnch 
16 - git branch <name of branch> creat new branch
17 - git checkout <name of branch> switched branch
18 - git branch -d <name of branch> del.?remove branch
19 - git branch -D <name of branch> del.?remove branch
20 - git checkout master -- switched to master branch
21 - git merge <name of branch> merge branch to master
22 - git log ---verfiy the merge
23 - git stash 
24 - git stash list ---> checking list of stash
25 - git stash apply stasj@{}
26 - git stash clear ---> remove all stash file
27 - git reset <name of file> ---> file is take back from satging area
28 - git reset . --->file is take back from satging area
29 - git reset --hard ---->file is take back from satging area also the working area
30 - git reset --soft
this all cammand what i learn from lecture video
